<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Onboarding Checklist</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #0A0A0A;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 0;
        }
        .page-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .start-date-banner {
            background-color: #171717;
            color: #FAFAFA;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .start-date-banner strong {
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .checklist-box {
            background-color: #F5F5F5;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .checklist-box h3 {
            margin: 0 0 14px 0;
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #171717;
        }
        .checklist-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #525252;
        }
        .checklist-item:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .check-icon {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
            min-width: 18px;
            border: 2px solid #D4D4D4;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-right: 12px;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }
        .hr-contact {
            background-color: #F5F5F5;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .hr-contact h3 {
            margin: 0 0 8px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #171717;
        }
        .hr-contact p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #525252;
        }
        .hr-contact a {
            color: #171717;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
            color: #737373;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">Employee Management System</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h1 class="page-title">Your Onboarding Checklist</h1>

            <p>Dear {{employeeName}},</p>

            <p>Welcome to the team! To help you get settled in smoothly, here is your onboarding checklist. Please complete all items before or shortly after your first day.</p>

            <div class="start-date-banner">
                Your first day: <strong>{{startDate}}</strong>
            </div>

            <div class="checklist-box">
                <h3>Tasks to Complete:</h3>
                {{#each checklistItems}}
                <div class="checklist-item">
                    <span class="check-icon"></span>
                    <span>{{this}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/each}}
            </div>

            <p>Make sure each item is completed and confirmed. Your manager or HR representative will follow up with you during your first week to review your progress.</p>

            <div class="hr-contact">
                <h3>Your HR Contact:</h3>
                <p><strong>{{hrContactName}}</strong><br>
                <a href="mailto:{{hrContactEmail}}">{{hrContactEmail}}</a></p>
                <p style="margin-top: 6px; color: #737373;">Feel free to reach out for any onboarding questions or assistance.</p>
            </div>

            <p>We are thrilled to have you on board and look forward to your first day!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message from the Employee Management System.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
